{"tid":470140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★優秀IT--登入股票戶口誤闖他人帳戶","createTime":"2017-11-16T04:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T04:46:32.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"68db446c805eb10e0b6aac9d18c79aa8a91b4043","tid":470140,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:32:28.000Z","msg":"用手機買賣股票時，登入了別人的戶口，可以點做？有股民近日反映，以手機登入本港一間以低廉佣金作見稱證券行&lrm;的個人股票戶口時，赫見戶中裏的持貨並不是自己購入的股票。頓時大嚇一跳：「以為有人用緊我帳號，幫我賺埋錢！」細看之下才發現竟登入了他人的戶口，他人帳戶內合共近15萬現金結餘及股票受亦無所遁形。證券公司指正跟進事件，懷疑事主誤入釣魚網站。<br />\n<br />\n有男股民向東網反映，於周一(13日)早上9時許，以其手機登入其證券帳戶，嘗試數次及轉換了另一部手機亦無法登入。正當他以為系統出問題之際，他終成功登入，但卻發現，他竟用預先紀錄(cookie)在手機的帳戶及密碼，成功登入他人的帳戶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171116/bkn-20171116111501148-1116_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171116%2Fbkn-20171116111501148-1116_00822_001.html&d=f5FGq3ggdxP5DuSvVviHgcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=15d21fb4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171116/bkn-20171116111501148-1116_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e63727e0ca6260590c68799669371331fa84e9b2","tid":470140,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f8b2b9a4835452bc9580695dcc0c5da49a8755","tid":470140,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2fff05f5c68f759c680f48ba5a6328e49fa955","tid":470140,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:44:00.000Z","msg":"Hk no it"},{"pid":"9b49816271265fde2302b8fb341c9504cb09c89c","tid":470140,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:44:34.000Z","msg":"HK No IT"},{"pid":"ee9fea873b95e206fa6adeaa2dd36441844293ec","tid":470140,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:45:15.000Z","msg":"IT狗：Login到咪得，梗係有bug，睇下ios11<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec660c5c39155112fcfa0c5a5e424d9cf7b65360","tid":470140,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:46:32.000Z","msg":"Gay cook ios 11竪立壞榜樣<br />\n<br />\n有bug是應份的<br />\n<br />\n垃圾apple"}]}